#Morocco: 0.5 million people (1.4% of the population) received the second dose of the #COVID19 #vaccine. 
10.5% of the population received at least 1dose (3.88 million people).
🇲🇦 Ranks 24th in the world for doses per 100 people (11.5 doses) & 15th for total doses (4.2 million). https://t.co/HpvGUrcYdT
